### 2. 鍐欏叆鏂囦欢 (Base64)

灏?base64 缂栫爜鐨勫唴瀹瑰啓鍏ユ寚瀹氭枃浠惰矾寰勩€?

**璇锋眰:**
```
POST /api/writefile?path=/var/mobile/test.txt&append=false
Content-Type: text/plain

<base64-encoded-content>
```

**鍙傛暟:**
| 鍙傛暟 | 绫诲瀷 | 蹇呭～ | 璇存槑 |
|------|------|------|------|
| path | string | 鏄?| 鐩爣鏂囦欢璺緞 |
| append | boolean | 鍚?| 鏄惁杩藉姞妯″紡锛岄粯璁?`false` |

**璇锋眰浣?**
- base64 缂栫爜鐨勬枃浠跺唴瀹?

**鍝嶅簲:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "path": "/var/mobile/test.txt",
  "bytes": 1024
}
```

**绀轰緥:**
```bash
# 鍐欏叆鏂囨湰鏂囦欢锛堜腑鏂囨敮鎸侊級
echo -n "浣犲ソ锛屼笘鐣岋紒" | base64 | curl -X POST \
  "http://192.168.1.100:8182/api/writefile?path=/var/mobile/test.txt" \
  -H "Content-Type: text/plain" \
  --data-binary @-

# 杩藉姞鍐呭
echo -n "杩藉姞鐨勫唴瀹? | base64 | curl -X POST \
  "http://192.168.1.100:8182/api/writefile?path=/var/mobile/test.txt&append=true" \
  -H "Content-Type: text/plain" \
  --data-binary @-
```

```python
import requests
import base64

content = "浣犲ソ锛屼笘鐣岋紒Hello World!"
encoded = base64.b64encode(content.encode()).decode()

response = requests.post(
    "http://192.168.1.100:8182/api/writefile?path=/var/mobile/test.txt",
    data=encoded,
    headers={"Content-Type": "text/plain"}
)
print(response.json())
```

